word_mean_info__list.difference: 主要指模仿他人或他物的样子，假装具有他人或他物的特点。
常和pretend换用，一般指言行上的“装做，假装”如装无知、悲哀；装死、疯或装做睡眠等。
指公开表示的与心里想的与客观实际不符合，含公开承认其虚假的意味。

bilingual.source: Spread out your arms and pretend to fly.
bilingual.target: 张开你的手臂假装飞翔。

bilingual.source: Flapping like a giant flag, which I pretend is mine.
bilingual.target: 像一面巨大的旗帜一样飘动，我假装它是我的。

bilingual.source: Which I can roll into a ball and pretend it isn't there.
bilingual.target: 我可以把它卷成一个球，假装它不存在。

bilingual.source: I pretend that I am a travel agent which means that I can carry out surveillance.
bilingual.target: 我假装自己是旅行社代理，这意味着我可以进行监视。

bilingual.source: He pretend to be sick to avoid work.
bilingual.target: 他假装生病来逃避工作。

bilingual.source: He pretend to be interested in the topic.
bilingual.target: 他假装对这个话题感兴趣。
我们不能假装什么都没发生。

bilingual.source: Let's pretend we are on a tropical island.
bilingual.target: 让我们假装我们在一个热带岛屿上。

bilingual.source: You can't just pretend the problem doesn't exist.
bilingual.target: 你不能只是假装问题不存在。

yingyinNormal.en: We tolerate discrimination and we pretend that opportunity is equal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们容忍歧视 假装机会是平等的。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《Facebook COO谢丽尔·桑德伯格哈佛演讲》

yingyinNormal.en: I'll pretend I didn't hear it. I'd rather you pretend I didn't say it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我会假装没听见。我宁愿你假装我没说过。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't know what you are talking about. It's just pretend. We're playing a game. Oh, I see. You want pretend water. Yes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不知道你们在说什么。这只是假装的，我们在玩游戏。哦，我知道了，你想要假装的水。是的。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, it's the ducks. They always turn up when we have a picnic. We've got pretend orange juice. And we've got pretend cake.
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢,是鸭子们呀!我们每次出来的时候总是能够见到他们。我们可以假装来喝橙汁。我们还可以假装吃蛋糕。

yingyinNormal.en: It does look rather yummy. Oh, let's pretend it was on the list.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就假装它也在清单上吧。

yingyinNormal.en: I've lived with it my whole life. You don't have to pretend.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我从出生就是这样。你不用假装哄我开心。

yingyinNormal.en: I know you've been melancholy. I don't pretend to know why.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道你心情不好，我也不会假装知道原因。

yingyinNormal.en: George, let's dress up and pretend to be Mummy and Daddy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治，我们把这些穿上，假装是爸爸和妈妈吧。

yingyinNormal.en: All right, I'm gonna tell you again. Pretend you haven't heard it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那我再跟你说一遍。你假装没听过就好啦。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, let's pretend it was on the list. Chocolate cake. Hurray!
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢，让我们假装它就在清单上吧。巧克力蛋糕。太棒了！

yingyinNormal.en: It's a classic scam. You pretend you know someone and then borrow money.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是经典的诈骗方式，假装认识对方然后借钱。

yingyinNormal.en: If my owner comes, put on the hood and pretend to be me. Okay, thank you!
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果我主人过来，戴上眼罩，假装是我。好的，谢谢！

yingyinNormal.en: It does look rather yummy. Oh, let's pretend it was on the list. Chocolate cake. Hurray!
yingyinNormal.zh: 就假装它也在清单上吧。巧克力蛋糕。好吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you coming in, Petro? I want a pretend sleeping a bit more. OK.
yingyinNormal.zh: 快进来吧，佩德罗？我还想再玩一会假装睡觉的游戏。那好吧！

yingyinNormal.en: It's all right, Sheldon. I will just pretend that Leonard's not withholding information.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没事的，谢尔顿，我会假装莱纳德没叫你瞒着我。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, don't apologize. Yeah. It just makes it a lot harder to pretend it never happened.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不必道歉。是啊，这让我们更难假装这事从未发生过。

yingyinNormal.en: Mummy Pig is home. Mummy. Mummy's here. Quick. Pretend nothing has happened.
yingyinNormal.zh: 猪妈妈回来了。妈妈！妈妈回来了！快，假装什么事都没发生。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't pretend you're not enjoying this. Being back. Being a hero again. Don't be stupid.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别假装你没在享受这一切 回归，做回英雄。别傻了。

yingyinNormal.en: Then let's not pretend to unite the party, let's unite the party behind this legislation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那就别假装全党统一了，让全党统一支持这项法案吧。

yingyinNormal.en: See? That's a great smile. Easy. Natural. Now, pretend I have a camera.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看吧？那个笑容非常灿烂，放轻松，自然一点，现在假装我手上拿了照相机。

word_usage.usage:
pretend作动词时，既可作及物动词，又可作不及物动词。
作及物动词时，其后可接名词、代词、动词不定式（to do的形式）或由that引导的从句，如：I don't pretend to be a scholar. 我不假装是个学者。
pretend作形容词时，常用于名词之前，修饰该名词，常为儿童用语，如：pretend cakes

examination_example.sentence: The results obtained by researchers who <highlight>pretended</highlight> to be patients seeking help from telemedicine providers are disturbing.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 假装成病人的研究人员向远程医疗服务提供者寻求帮助，得到的结果令人不安。

examination_example.sentence: Hale claimed for the rest of her life that "Some other people <highlight>pretended</highlight> that someone else wrote the poem".
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在他的余生中，Hale一直声称：“有些人假装这首诗是别人写的”。
